# Oratio Clinic – Medical Recording Web Application (v2)

A SvelteKit web application for dental healthcare medical recording with three roles (Admin, Kasir, Dokter), integrating SatuSehat APIs and Snowstorm SNOMED-CT terminology. Deployed via Docker on Synology NAS.

---

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Environment Configuration**: Defaults to **Staging** SatuSehat credentials. Production activated via `SATUSEHAT_ENV=production`.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Tech Stack**: Drizzle ORM, `jose` (JWT), `pdfmake` (PDF), `papaparse` (CSV), `chart.js` (doctor analytics), custom SVG odontogram.

> [!WARNING]
> **Credentials**: SatuSehat secrets stored in `.env` / Docker secrets only — **never committed to git**.

> [!CAUTION]
> **No HTTPS**: LAN-only (`192.168.100.118`). Add HTTPS reverse proxy if ever exposed to WAN.

---

