### 5. Kasir Module

#### [NEW] [kasir/+page.svelte](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/routes/kasir/+page.svelte)

**Appointment List + ★ Queue Board**:

★ **Insightful Queue Management**:
- **Visual queue board** (Kanban-style columns): Waiting → In Progress → Discharged → Completed
- Each card shows: queue number, patient name, doctor, wait time elapsed, status badge
- Cards are color-coded by wait time (green <15min, yellow 15-30min, red >30min)
- **Drag-disabled** (status changes only via workflow), but provides instant visual overview
- **Summary bar** at top: "3 waiting · 2 in progress · 5 completed today"
- Auto-refresh every 30 seconds

**Data Table** (toggle between queue board and table view):
- Columns: Queue#, Patient Name, NIK, Doctor, Status, Arrived Time, Duration
- Filters: date range, doctor, status
- Status badges with color coding

#### [NEW] [kasir/new-patient/+page.svelte](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/routes/kasir/new-patient/+page.svelte)

**New Patient Registration Form** — ★ **Auto-queues patient on submission**:

| Section | Fields |
|---------|--------|
| Identity | NIK*, Nama Lengkap*, Birth Date*, Birthplace, Gender |
| Family | Nomor KK |
| Address | Address*, Province*, City*, District*, Village*, RT*, RW* |
| Contact | Handphone, Email |
| Personal | Marital Status (S/M/W/D), Citizenship (WNI/WNA), Language (BCP-47) |
| Medical | Golongan Darah*, Rhesus, Status Kehamilan |
| Vitals | Tekanan Darah (XX/XX mmHg) |
| Assignment | Kode Dokter* (dropdown, ★ shows only doctors on-shift today per `doctor_shifts`) |
| Condition | Keluhan Utama (SNOMED autocomplete, 404684003) |
| History | Riwayat Penyakit Pribadi / Keluarga (Snowstorm) |
| Medication | Riwayat Pengobatan (KFA search) |
| Allergy | Substance (Snowstorm) + Reaction (fixed dropdown, 30 items) |

**On submit**:
1. Creates patient record
2. Creates encounter (status=Planned) with auto-generated queue number
3. ★ **Patient immediately appears on the Queue Board** — kasir sees them in "Waiting" column
4. Generates patient profile PDF
5. Redirects to queue board with success toast: "Pasien {name} ditambahkan ke antrian #{queue}"

#### [NEW] [kasir/existing-patient/+page.svelte](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/routes/kasir/existing-patient/+page.svelte)

**Existing Patient Appointment Form**:
- ★ Search by **medical record number (ID), NIK, or patient name** (fuzzy search)
- Results shown in searchable dropdown with: ID, Name, NIK preview
- Display patient info (read-only) after selection
- Input: Kode Dokter* (filtered to on-shift), optional referral source
- On submit: creates encounter, auto-queues → appears on queue board

