### 6. Dokter Module

#### [NEW] [dokter/+page.svelte](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/routes/dokter/+page.svelte)

**Doctor Dashboard**: queue, history, referrals. Click patient → encounter form.

★ **Shift Countdown Timer**: A persistent header bar showing the doctor's current shift end time and a **live countdown** (e.g., "Shift ends at 17:00 — 2h 34m remaining"). Updates every minute via client-side `setInterval`. When <30 minutes remaining, the badge pulses amber; when <10 minutes, it turns red. If the doctor is outside their shift hours, it shows "No active shift" with the next scheduled shift time.

#### ★ [NEW] [dokter/analytics/+page.svelte](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/routes/dokter/analytics/+page.svelte)

**Doctor Analytics & Visualization Page** — insightful monitoring dashboard:

| Widget | Visualization | Purpose |
|--------|--------------|---------|
| **Patient Volume** | Line chart (daily/weekly/monthly) | Track patient flow trends |
| **Treatment Breakdown** | Doughnut chart by ICD-9-CM procedure | See most common treatments |
| **Top Diagnoses** | Horizontal bar chart by ICD-10 | Understand diagnostic patterns |
| **Revenue Summary** | Stacked bar chart (items × quantity) | Monitor revenue contribution |
| **Avg. Treatment Time** | Gauge/KPI card | Track efficiency (In Progress duration) |
| **Appointment Completion** | Pie chart (Completed vs Cancelled/Discontinued) | Monitor completion rates |
| **Referral Flow** | Sankey or table (referred-from / referred-to) | Track inter-doctor referrals |
| **Recent Activity** | Timeline feed (last 10 encounters) | Quick overview of recent work |

**Design principles**:
- **At-a-glance**: KPI cards at top (patients today, this week, this month, avg time)
- **Filterable**: date range picker to narrow data
- **Clean visuals**: uses `chart.js` with the doctor's role-specific color palette
- **No data overload**: defaults to "This Month" view, only shows meaningful metrics
- **Actionable**: click on a chart segment → filters the encounter list below

#### [NEW] [dokter/[encounterId]/+page.svelte](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/routes/dokter/%5BencounterId%5D/+page.svelte)

**Single-Page Encounter Form** with two modes (SOAP / SOAP-WHO).

★ **Patient Context Sidebar** (collapsible, pinned to the right):
While filling the form, the doctor sees a side panel with:
- **Patient Info**: name, age, gender, blood type, allergies (highlighted), pregnancy status
- **Past Encounters**: accordion list of previous encounters by this doctor — each showing date, diagnosis (ICD-10), procedures (ICD-9-CM), SOAP summary
- **Past Prescriptions**: medications prescribed in prior visits
- **Referral Source**: if this patient was referred, shows the referring doctor's notes
- The panel auto-loads when the encounter page opens and is scrollable independently from the form

##### Mode: SOAP-WHO — Odontogram

★ **Odontogram follows PDGI Standard** (Panduan Rekam Medis Dokter Gigi):
- **Layout**: Upper arch (maxilla) teeth 18-11, 21-28 on top row; Lower arch (mandible) teeth 48-41, 31-38 on bottom row. Child dentition: 55-51, 61-65 / 85-81, 71-75.
- **FDI Notation**: International two-digit numbering system
- **Each tooth rendered as 5-surface SVG** (cross/diamond shape):
  - Center: Occlusal (O)
  - Top: Buccal/Labial (B)
  - Bottom: Lingual/Palatal (L)
  - Left: Mesial (M)
  - Right: Distal (D)
- **Condition symbols drawn on teeth** per PDGI standard (e.g., filled surface = restorasi, X = extraction, etc.)
- **Click** any surface → opens detail modal for that tooth
- **Multi-select**: hold Shift to select multiple teeth surfaces simultaneously
- **Summary table** below the chart shows all filled-in teeth conditions

**Status Logic**: Opening → In Progress, Close without submit → On Hold, Submit → Discharged.

**PDF Generation**: SOAP → SOAP PDF; SOAP-WHO → Odontogram PDF (★ PDGI standard layout with teeth diagram + condition legend) + SOAP PDF.

#### [NEW] [dokter/patient/[patientId]/+page.svelte](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/routes/dokter/patient/%5BpatientId%5D/+page.svelte)

Patient detail: ID, demographics, medical history, encounter history for this doctor.

