### 10. UI Design System — ★ Role-Specific Color Palettes

#### [NEW] [app.css](file:///C:/Users/rephr/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/oratio-dental/src/app.css)

★ **Three distinct color palettes** — modern, calming, seamless:

| Role | Primary | Secondary | Accent | Sidebar | Mood |
|------|---------|-----------|--------|---------|------|
| **Admin** | Slate Blue `#6366F1` | Cool Gray `#F1F5F9` | Violet `#8B5CF6` | Dark Slate `#1E293B` | Professional, authoritative |
| **Kasir** | Sage Green `#10B981` | Warm Cream `#FEFCE8` | Teal `#14B8A6` | Deep Forest `#064E3B` | Calm, efficient, organized |
| **Dokter** | Ocean Blue `#3B82F6` | Soft White `#F8FAFC` | Sky `#38BDF8` | Navy `#1E3A5F` | Clinical, trustworthy, focused |

**Shared design tokens**:
- Typography: Inter (Google Fonts), clean hierarchies
- Border-radius: 12px cards, 8px inputs
- Shadows: subtle, layered (`0 1px 3px`, `0 4px 6px`)
- Micro-animations: 200ms ease transitions, hover lifts, loading skeletons
- Responsive: tablet + desktop optimized for clinic use
- Sidebar detects role via CSS custom properties set by layout

